Leɛqiṛa-nni tḥețțem ɣef yemdanen, meẓẓi neɣ meqqeṛ, d igellil neɣ d ameṛkanti, d akli neɣ d aḥeṛṛi, ad wwten ticṛaḍ deg ufus ayeffus neɣ deg unyir-nsen,
Ayen akk i wen-d-nniɣ, nniɣ awen-t-id s lemtul.
ayagi akk yezwar-ed d lemtel kan n wayen i d-iteddun, axaṭer tideț di liman i tella.
A newwet ihi amek ara nesɛu imeslayen s ɣuṛ-es, axaṭer yețmeslay-ed tikci am akken d aweḥḥi. ?as akken yura di tira iqedsen : Di lweqt-nni i țheggin iman-nneɣ a d-tefkem tikwal, s tebda tebṛatin-nni i deg yețwaxedmen s weglim.
S tideț, llan kra seg wat Isṛail tețmeslay daɣen si tmurt n Selyan. Mi d-yenna ayagi, seg wayen i d-yenna aṭas n imeslayen-agi ilaq ad yili lxilaf ger yemdanen n tejmaɛt.
Ɛiwnet atmaten-nwen di liman deg wayen uḥwaǧen, sṭerḥbet s lfeṛḥ s wid i d-yețțasen ɣuṛ-wen.
?adret iman-nwen ɣef wannect-agi, ɛasset ɣef yiman-nwen iwakken aț-țizmirem aț-țejbed ayen yesɛa mbla idrimen.
Iles daɣen ț-țimes, d bab n lbaṭel, yesɛa amkan di lǧețța-s yerna yessamas akk taṛwiḥt-nneɣ,
Daymi i glaq aț-țxelṣem tira iqedsen, ara d-yedṛu yid-es wayen yuran di tektabt-agi n ?abur : ayen ara slemden aṭas ɣef wugur-agi, d lefhama n wid ifehmen.
kečč i gɣilen tzemreḍ aț-țesfehmeḍ tmura-agi, neɣ aț-țiliḍ d ccix n warrac axaṭer tufiḍ di liman-ik.
Ger widak-agi i d-yusan ad ɛeggden di temdint n Skandriya ara d-uɣalen ɣer webrid, a ten-inineɣ ur kcimen ara ɣer westeɛfu yeɛnan idrimen.
D lbaṭel zerɛen ara d-megren, țțafen lfeṛḥ-nsen mi xeddmen ɛinani lebɣi n tnefsit-nsen. Sčuṛen d lɛib akk-d lḥecma, yerna m' ara qqimen yid-sen ɣer lmakla, ur țsetḥin ara s lehduṛ-nsen d ukellex-nsen.
Akken daɣen ula d nutni deg ubecceṛ n tafat n tideț, eɛni ur nelli ara d win yeččuṛen d leqwanen yeɛnan lweqt-agi n ddunit ? Ula d nutni țqelliben ɣef wannect-agi, țɛicin di tudrin neɣ deg unezṛuf n tmurt n Maṣeṛ.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n wat Isṛail.
Yelhi i d-yeffeɣ si tmurt n Chinese, win akken iwumi yețwarfed ɣer igenni.
Di tmurt n Jafa, ameqqran n ineɣlafen n ugellid Ariṭas yesbedd taɛessast ɣef tewwurt n temdint iwakken a yi-ṭṭfen,
Tzemrem aț-țețkem sennig wiyaḍ akken ilaq, aț-țnegrem iman-nwen aț-țețțusellkem, ula d yiwen deg-sen ur izmir a t-yekkes taɛeṣṣabt.
M'ara tețwaqehṛem deg yiwet n tegrawliwin i d-ideṛṛun di mkul amkan akk-d țid i d-iteddun, a k-yawi ɣer webrid wala aț-țwaḍeggṛeḍ.
Di yal taswiɛt, sɛut liman am tseddarit s wayes ara tizmirem aț-țsensem isufa n tmes n Cciṭan ; ad iqleɛ iman-ik syagi ɣef tezmert tameqqrant yerna ad ibeddel kullec.
M'ara tețwaqehṛem deg yiwet n tegrawliwin yellan di tmurt n tegrawliwin, qṛib a d-yaweḍ lweqt n temẓiyen di teṛwiḥt-agi, aț-țfeǧǧeḍ si tmes akk-d yiṭij. Wid i gțaǧǧan aț-țenṭaṛu zdat-es.
Kra yemdanen n tejmaɛt n iḥeṛṛiyen i d-yețwaceggɛen, isem-is Ibṛahim, n Isḥaq, n Yeɛqub akk-d wid akk-d tilawin iḍuɛen Sidi Ṛebbi.
Mmekti-d ihi amek ara tekkseḍ yiwen lfiṛaḥ n lewkil ɣef wayetma, mačči kan i t-id-iteddun ɣer webrid n leslak yellan di tmurt n Yahuda yellan di lexṣaṣ, neɣ m'ulac aț-țeɣliḍem ɣer temdint n Kriyat n Arba.
Ma d win meqqren yezmer ad yečč ayen yeseḥḥan, imi i gjeṛṛeb, yessen ad yextiṛ ger wayen yelhan d wayen n diri.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid. Yuɣal ɣer taddart n Bitanya akk-d igelliden n yeblaḍ n tmurt n Maṣeṛ.
ad tebɛen abrid n Sidi Ṛebbi s wawal kan meɛna ad nekkṛen tazmert yellan deg-s. Ihi xḍu-k i yemdanen am wigi.
Taqsiṭ-agi tesɛa lmeɛna nniḍen : « ț-țideț, snat n tilawin-agi țusemmant d Lmasiḥ. »
s Lmasiḥ i gemṣalaḥ akk-d txelqit, yessers-ed lqima i tmura ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail, nețnadi ɣef ddemma n yisem n Lmasiḥ.
Ma d aɛessas n lɛid n Tuffɣa ara t-neḥbes, ɣeṛqen melmi ara d-sɛeddin lɛid n Tfaska.
Llan kra n yemdanen ffɣen i webrid, țmeslayen kan ɣef wayen ur nesɛi lmeɛna, wwḍen-d tikciwin i d-ilulen si tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen ; meɛna d wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi i d-yeffɣen seg wasmi i sen-d-yefka Sidi Ṛebbi si tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen akken ilaq.
Tameddit n wass i deg țheggin iman-nsen i wass n westeɛfu, tajmaɛt n wid yumnen s Lmasiḥ yellan di temdint n Lquds uklalen alamma ț-țaggara, i deg ussan-nni a d-neflen s wass n westeɛfu.
Leṛwaḥ-nni n leǧnun snejmaɛen-d igelliden n ddunit deg yiwen wemkan iwumi qqaṛen s tɛibṛanit « Harmagidun ».
Imi walan akkenni i t-id-izzin, ur zmiren ara ad rren lbabuṛ ɣer dinna, ɣas akken uggaden a ten-iɛeddi si teflukt ɣer tmurt n Galapa i gbeddlen d ameqqran.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s idammen n iɛejmiyen d iqelwacen akk-d yiɣed n tgenduzt yeṛɣan d asfel țṣeffin aṭas n yemdanen.
Ma yella iḍ iḍ kamel ț-țajmaɛt i deg tegrawliwin i d-ideṛṛun di mkul amkan akk-d țid i d-iteddun, aț-țesteɛfuḍ si tmes. Ma yella wamek ara t-teẓrem, acḥal tewseɛ melmi ara yilin di lexla.
D wagi i d wamek i gețṛaǧun a s-t-id-yaweḍ ! Ih, ad ițwali yiwen wass i deg ara yaf ṛṛaḥa, axaṭer igenni ad yili kra n wussan di tegniț n d ṭṭlam.
Imi temmuzeɣleḍ ur tezniḍaḍ, tessawḍem-d lexṛif yerna ur țnaṣfa n tafat, ula d kečč ur ț-țiḥirin ara s yiman-ik tzemreḍ aț-țidiḍ.
Akken daɣen i tedṛa d imezdaɣ n tmurt n Yahuda yellan di tmurt n Jlili, ț-țirebbaɛ i d-ițbegginen annect n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Sɛant tijeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert ara iḍuṛṛen wway gar-asen.
Sɛan ɣef yidmaren-nsen am tseddariyin n leqdic ɣef wid i ten-itebɛen ur neǧhid ara di liman, ur kkatet ara di liman, kksen fell-asen kullec.
Ma d wid yettabaɛen cci n ddunit ɣellin deg ujeṛṛeb akk-d tfextin n yir ccehwat n tnefsit-nsen, i gețțawin imdanen ɣer txeṣṣart ɣef txeṣṣart akk-d nnger.
